00:31:18.221 --> 00:31:18.720
Suggestions?

00:31:22.110 --> 00:31:22.866
Yep?

00:31:22.866 --> 00:31:24.657
AUDIENCE: The assumption
of uniform density

00:31:24.657 --> 00:31:26.360
in a phase transition?

00:31:26.360 --> 00:31:27.580
PROFESSOR: Right.

00:31:27.580 --> 00:31:31.030
That's the picture
that I put over here.

00:31:31.030 --> 00:31:34.510
If I draw the box that
corresponds to what

00:31:34.510 --> 00:31:37.750
is happening over there,
what's going on in the box?

00:31:37.750 --> 00:31:40.100
So there is a box.

00:31:40.100 --> 00:31:44.860
I have particles in it
and in the region where

00:31:44.860 --> 00:31:47.640
this nonsense is
happening, what is actually

00:31:47.640 --> 00:31:48.930
happening in reality?

00:31:48.930 --> 00:31:51.390
What is actually
