00:31:51.390 --> 00:31:54.380
is that I get some
of the particles

00:31:54.380 --> 00:31:58.220
to condense into
liquid drops somewhere

00:31:58.220 --> 00:31:59.880
and then there's
basically the rest

00:31:59.880 --> 00:32:03.950
of them floating
around as a gas.

00:32:03.950 --> 00:32:05.360
Right?

00:32:05.360 --> 00:32:12.560
So clearly I cannot, for this
configuration that I have over

00:32:12.560 --> 00:32:18.730
here, calculate energy
