00:32:33.885 --> 00:32:34.385
OK?

00:32:37.270 --> 00:32:41.120
So what do we do?

00:32:41.120 --> 00:32:44.100
I want to carry out
this calculation.

00:32:44.100 --> 00:32:46.490
I want to stay as
much as possible

00:32:46.490 --> 00:32:50.070
and within this framework
and I can do it,

00:32:50.070 --> 00:32:52.679
but I need to do
one other thing.

00:32:52.679 --> 00:32:53.345
Any suggestions?

00:32:58.860 --> 00:32:59.930
Yes?

00:32:59.930 --> 00:33:03.670
AUDIENCE: Try to describe
both densities simultaneously?

00:33:03.670 --> 00:33:06.695
PROFESSOR: Try to
