00:59:13.960 --> 00:59:17.280
and the statement is
that along the isotherm

00:59:17.280 --> 00:59:21.220
this derivative
has to be negative.

00:59:21.220 --> 00:59:28.420
So generically what
I have is that d P

00:59:28.420 --> 00:59:33.430
by d V for a physical
isotherm has to be negative

00:59:33.430 --> 00:59:37.390
and indeed the reason we
don't like that portion

00:59:37.390 --> 00:59:41.890
is because it violates
