01:00:29.275 --> 01:00:34.510
that V cubed, I will be
able to pick a delta V such

01:00:34.510 --> 01:00:37.610
that the sine will be
violated by the delta V

01:00:37.610 --> 01:00:40.290
of positive or
delta V of negative.

01:00:40.290 --> 01:00:45.990
And clearly what it says is
